GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_SeparationPrincipleProductVsOrg> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_SeparationPrincipleProductVsOrg> a narr:Digest ;
